1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:09,000
Taking walks and playing games when there's sunny weather

2
00:00:09,000 --> 00:00:15,000
If there's rain, they're singing songs or reading books together

3
00:00:15,000 --> 00:00:21,000
Every day just has a way of feeling extra lucky

4
00:00:21,000 --> 00:00:26,000
When you spend it with a friend, just like Bjorn and Bucky

5
00:00:26,000 --> 00:00:29,000
Just like Bjorn and Bucky!

6
00:00:30,000 --> 00:00:32,000
A journey!

7
00:00:38,000 --> 00:00:41,000
Good morning, Bjorn! What are you doing?

8
00:00:41,000 --> 00:00:45,000
Bucky, hi there! I'm just getting stuff ready to go

9
00:00:45,000 --> 00:00:49,000
You mean, you're going on a trip? Can I come too?

10
00:00:49,000 --> 00:00:52,000
Why not? Come on along!

11
00:00:52,000 --> 00:00:55,000
I just love to travel the world, but not on foot

12
00:00:55,000 --> 00:00:59,000
Walking's too slow, plus you can't carry enough stuff, plus you don't see a lot

13
00:00:59,000 --> 00:01:01,000
Plus plus you can get lost!

14
00:01:01,000 --> 00:01:04,000
We won't get lost when I bring this compass with us

15
00:01:04,000 --> 00:01:07,000
Awesome! I've got an idea!

16
00:01:07,000 --> 00:01:09,000
Rope, please tell me you have some!

17
00:01:10,000 --> 00:01:12,000
Excellent! That'll work!

18
00:01:12,000 --> 00:01:15,000
Come over to my place in the morning and bring your stuff!

19
00:01:15,000 --> 00:01:17,000
Time to be awesome!

20
00:01:17,000 --> 00:01:22,000
Hi Bucky!

21
00:01:22,000 --> 00:01:25,000
Oh, wait a minute! What's floating in your yard?

22
00:01:25,000 --> 00:01:28,000
It's for us! A hot air balloon for our trip!

23
00:01:28,000 --> 00:01:33,000
Come on! Climb on board! It's time for us to fly!

24
00:01:33,000 --> 00:01:38,000
I don't think I'll be traveling by air! No way! I am not a flying bear!

25
00:01:38,000 --> 00:01:45,000
Why not? The balloon will carry us and all our stuff and there's no chance we'll get lost because we can see everything from up here!

26
00:01:45,000 --> 00:01:49,000
Well, even if you're right about all that, it's bad weather for flying today!

27
00:01:49,000 --> 00:01:52,000
Ah, I get it! You're afraid of flying, right?

28
00:01:52,000 --> 00:01:55,000
What? I am not afraid of flying!

29
00:01:55,000 --> 00:01:56,000
Are you sure?

30
00:01:56,000 --> 00:01:59,000
Problem!

31
00:01:59,000 --> 00:02:02,000
Bjorn! Bjorn! I'm really scared!

32
00:02:02,000 --> 00:02:06,000
Hey! Bucky!

33
00:02:06,000 --> 00:02:09,000
Please do something, Bjorn! Help me!

34
00:02:09,000 --> 00:02:15,000
Hang on! It's a hurricane!

35
00:02:15,000 --> 00:02:19,000
I hate flying!

36
00:02:19,000 --> 00:02:22,000
I'm not loving it either!

37
00:02:22,000 --> 00:02:24,000
Whoa!

38
00:02:24,000 --> 00:02:25,000
Whoa!

39
00:02:25,000 --> 00:02:26,000
Ow! Ow!

40
00:02:28,000 --> 00:02:31,000
Listen! Turn us around, Bjorn!

41
00:02:31,000 --> 00:02:34,000
How? It's your runaway balloon!

42
00:02:34,000 --> 00:02:36,000
You're supposed to be steering it!

43
00:02:36,000 --> 00:02:37,000
Yikes!

44
00:02:37,000 --> 00:02:38,000
Ouch!

45
00:02:38,000 --> 00:02:39,000
My scarf!

46
00:02:40,000 --> 00:02:42,000
Bucky!

47
00:02:42,000 --> 00:02:53,000
Bucky! You gotta grab that thing! Come on! Grab onto that tower!

48
00:02:53,000 --> 00:02:54,000
What?

49
00:02:55,000 --> 00:02:57,000
Ah! Electric lines!

50
00:02:59,000 --> 00:03:00,000
Shocking!

51
00:03:00,000 --> 00:03:03,000
Look! Ducks! Help us, duckies!

52
00:03:03,000 --> 00:03:05,000
Bucky! We're flying south, I think!

53
00:03:05,000 --> 00:03:08,000
I haven't ever been this way before!

54
00:03:08,000 --> 00:03:12,000
How much longer are we gonna fly, Bjorn?

55
00:03:12,000 --> 00:03:16,000
Long as this big strong wind blows, we're gonna keep on flying!

56
00:03:17,000 --> 00:03:19,000
Sorry, house on a stick!

57
00:03:19,000 --> 00:03:21,000
I always wanted to ride this!

58
00:03:21,000 --> 00:03:22,000
Yeah!

59
00:03:23,000 --> 00:03:24,000
Aw!

60
00:03:24,000 --> 00:03:26,000
It's spinning fast!

61
00:03:26,000 --> 00:03:27,000
Hold your breath!

62
00:03:28,000 --> 00:03:30,000
Help us, you two!

63
00:03:30,000 --> 00:03:32,000
Whoa! Look at the cool crane!

64
00:03:33,000 --> 00:03:34,000
Watch out! Mountain!

65
00:03:34,000 --> 00:03:36,000
Correction! Volcano!

66
00:03:36,000 --> 00:03:39,000
Why are we still flying?

67
00:03:44,000 --> 00:03:47,000
Yeah, you were right. Balloon travel was a bad call.

68
00:03:47,000 --> 00:03:49,000
I guess that we better walk home.

69
00:03:49,000 --> 00:03:50,000
But where's home?

70
00:03:51,000 --> 00:03:54,000
We've flown so far, I don't know the way back!

71
00:03:55,000 --> 00:03:56,000
Well, I don't know how to get back!

72
00:03:56,000 --> 00:03:58,000
Don't you have your fancy compass?

73
00:03:58,000 --> 00:03:59,000
Well, yeah.

74
00:03:59,000 --> 00:04:03,000
Only it's still inside my backpack, which is back at your house!

75
00:04:03,000 --> 00:04:04,000
Ugh!

76
00:04:05,000 --> 00:04:08,000
What are we gonna do about this? I wanna go home!

77
00:04:08,000 --> 00:04:10,000
Bucky, guess what?

78
00:04:10,000 --> 00:04:12,000
I think you were right, my friend!

79
00:04:12,000 --> 00:04:15,000
We can travel in this balloon of yours!

80
00:04:15,000 --> 00:04:18,000
Because I just had a great idea!

81
00:04:18,000 --> 00:04:22,000
That was some great thinking, Bjorn!

82
00:04:22,000 --> 00:04:24,000
This is a great view, just lovely!

83
00:04:24,000 --> 00:04:26,000
Don't forget that I need directions!

84
00:04:27,000 --> 00:04:29,000
Do your job!

85
00:04:29,000 --> 00:04:30,000
Go left!

86
00:04:30,000 --> 00:04:32,000
Good! I see our volcano over there!

87
00:04:32,000 --> 00:04:35,000
Turn to the right now, then straight ahead!

88
00:04:35,000 --> 00:04:36,000
You're doing great!

89
00:04:36,000 --> 00:04:40,000
Come on, let's switch jobs, so I can do some flying too, Buck!

90
00:04:40,000 --> 00:04:45,000
Is it just me, or have I been pulling a lot longer than you did?

91
00:04:45,000 --> 00:04:46,000
Bjorn?

92
00:04:47,000 --> 00:04:48,000
Ooh, my scarf!

93
00:04:50,000 --> 00:04:51,000
Oh, look out!

94
00:04:51,000 --> 00:04:53,000
We're back at all those wires!

95
00:04:53,000 --> 00:04:54,000
Keep to the right!

96
00:04:55,000 --> 00:04:56,000
Yo!

97
00:04:56,000 --> 00:04:57,000
Bucky!

98
00:04:57,000 --> 00:04:58,000
Your other right!

99
00:05:01,000 --> 00:05:02,000
Oh!

100
00:05:02,000 --> 00:05:03,000
Hey!

101
00:05:03,000 --> 00:05:04,000
There's your house!

102
00:05:04,000 --> 00:05:05,000
Hooray!

103
00:05:05,000 --> 00:05:06,000
We made it!

104
00:05:06,000 --> 00:05:07,000
We made it!

105
00:05:09,000 --> 00:05:10,000
Yeah!

106
00:05:10,000 --> 00:05:12,000
Traveling is pretty awesome!

107
00:05:12,000 --> 00:05:14,000
Let's get lost up north tomorrow!

108
00:05:14,000 --> 00:05:15,000
Let's what?

109
00:05:19,000 --> 00:05:20,000
Bjorn?

110
00:05:20,000 --> 00:05:21,000
Why are you laughing?

111
00:05:21,000 --> 00:05:22,000
I'm serious!

112
00:05:22,000 --> 00:05:24,000
Bears don't have wings, right?

